    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in wonderful shape for its next adventure! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 28900.0,
