    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit retains its mechanical purity with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and a refreshed suspension geometry, providing the communicative steering and balanced 50/50 weight distribution this platform is famous for. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a driven machine, the powertrain is robust, offering visceral induction noise and linear power delivery throughout the rev range.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Reliable daily driver. Clean title. Routine maintenance complete. Interior well-maintained.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
